        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>General Secretary Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the federal government from creating or disseminating documents that refer to China's head of state as anything other than <i>General Secretary of the Chinese Communist Party </i>or <i>General Secretary</i>.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
